From 8a4af7e2fde16f2dc8d39e72f89ef4653ed3f442 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 13:52:37 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 37/84] Trace PDF claim lifecycle

A claim stood beside the stream,
But downloads cut short the dream.
So logs caught the race,
At the content_shell place,
Where PDFs leave render's regime.
---
 .../browser/pdf/pdf_viewer_stream_manager.cc  | 68 ++++++++++++++++++-
 ...esponse_interceptor_url_loader_throttle.cc | 29 ++++----
 2 files changed, 82 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)

diff --git a/chrome/browser/pdf/pdf_viewer_stream_manager.cc b/chrome/browser/pdf/pdf_viewer_stream_manager.cc
